                <DIV class="ReviewHeading">Amazon.com:</DIV>
                <span id="Label1"><i>Home Design from the Inside Out</i> takes an unusual approach to home design. Author  Robin Lennon does away with the standard pictures of lavish interiors and exteriors for you to duplicate in  your home, and instead focuses on determining which designs, arrangements, colors, and decorative details will work best for your home, regardless of current trends. Lennon shows you how to  make your house feel like home by offering a unique, self-empowering look at home design that places the greatest importance on your tastes, needs, and preferences. </span>
              
</td></tr></table>
