                    <span>This is a wonderful book to help you become self aware.  There are exercises that you can do to help you determine who you really are & what you really like.  There are a broad range of subjects covering this  book such as Feng Shui, & Color Therapy.  Awesome book!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Read it and decorate your way!</div>
