                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>1998-02-09</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>Finally not just another book about what you should do with your looks or your life. For me, Home Design From the Inside Out made sense of everyday life. Not extravagent lifestyles, or impossible metaphysical demands, but real life, creative, processes which I can practice. Robin Lennon doesn't simplify or reduce these time honored ideas, but uniquely invisions them for how we live today. I highly recomend this book for artists and designers and for anyone looking to revitalize their life design.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Feng Shui Bamboozle</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
