                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>1997-06-04</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>Robin Lennon must be a very put-together woman!  Her advice goes far beyond where to place furniture and which colors go well with others.  After reading HOME DESIGN FROM THE INSIDE OUT I found the courage to throw away ancient artifacts from my youth and teenage years that should have gone in the trash long ago!  I never thought a book about interior design would be so helpful in my personal life.  I learned how to "create a home for my heart", and express my soul and creativity through my surroundings.  Open ANY page, and you'll find yourself shaking your head "yes", she's right, I just needed some one to put it to me like that.  It's only $14.95, and nearly 300 pages long!  Forget that new CD and BUY THIS BOOK</span>
                  
              
